## 🧠 Key Concepts Glossary

| Concept | Simple Definition |
|---|---|
| **LLM** | Large Language Model — the AI brain (GPT-4, Claude, Gemini) |
| **API** | A way to call a service over HTTP — you know this! |
| **Prompt** | The instruction/question you send to the LLM |
| **Token** | ~0.75 words — how LLMs measure text length |
| **Context Window** | Max tokens an LLM can "see" at once |
| **Inference** | Running the model to get an answer |
| **RAG** | Retrieval-Augmented Generation — LLM + your private data |
| **Agent** | An LLM that can plan, use tools, and take actions |

